data.description: New Construction by Fischer Homes in the beautiful Twin Lakes community with the Wyatt Cambridge Cottage plan featuring a stunning kitchen with pantry, lots of cabinet space and quartz countertops. Spacious family room expands to light-filled morning room. Private Living area up front and rec room in the back of the home. Primary Suite with sitting room, private bath and walk-in closet. Three additional secondary bedrooms, loft, and hall bath. Back patio and two car garage.
